Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.49,0:00:08.24,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,我真是個笨蛋啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.73,0:00:11.09,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,明明一開始打算立刻趕他出去的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.76,0:00:13.69,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.00,0:00:16.74,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,她在那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.10,0:00:18.96,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,正好一個人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.06,0:00:21.40,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,好 決定了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.54,0:00:25.87,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,只要變回和孝太郎相遇之前的我就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.57,0:00:28.80,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,因為我不是一直那樣過來的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.90,0:00:30.02,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,那傢伙是敵人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.79,0:00:32.84,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,這麼想的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.46,0:00:33.92,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,就是現在
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,OP
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.39,0:02:27.06,title1,,0,0,0,,{\pos(176.532,138.666)\fad(500,500)}#05 「重要的護身符」
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.47,0:02:23.30,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,等等我
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.58,0:02:26.70,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,真是的 早苗那傢伙跑到哪去了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.52,0:02:29.20,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,都快中午了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.29,0:02:34.70,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,這裡也撲空了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.15,0:02:36.71,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,今天你一個人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.18,0:02:39.01,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,櫻庭學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.06,0:02:43.68,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,你好 昨天的幾位沒跟你在一起嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.27,0:02:46.69,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,今天有點事分開行動了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.46,0:02:48.92,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,發生什麼事了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.35,0:02:52.04,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,其實是…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.70,0:02:57.22,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,到哪里去了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.52,0:02:59.87,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,不要 別過來
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.98,0:03:02.55,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,你們幹什麼 放開我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.99,0:03:06.02,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,你們也是幽靈吧 到底想幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.40,0:03:08.07,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,抵抗也是沒用的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.26,0:03:11.04,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,它們是我們花錢雇來的亡魂
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.30,0:03:13.60,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,你們是昨天的變態
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.73,0:03:17.99,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,才不是變態 我們是幽靈獵人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.28,0:03:19.30,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,幽靈獵人?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.45,0:03:23.55,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,是的 捕捉幽靈來販賣正是我們的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.84,0:03:25.41,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,咦 你們要把我給…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.52,0:03:26.07,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.42,0:03:30.72,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,像你這樣高密度並且形狀穩定的幽靈是很寶貴的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.29,0:03:34.13,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,只要賣給那些感興趣的人 我們就能賺到一大筆錢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.95,0:03:42.51,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,不要 我不要被賣掉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.72,0:03:46.93,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼辦 得去救她才行
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.83,0:03:51.00,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,可是剛才好像看到很多奇怪的東西…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.19,0:03:55.68,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,我該怎麼辦才好 里見
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.07,0:03:59.03,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,有沒有誰 有沒有誰…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.59,0:04:03.06,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,如果你放棄了 我會覺得遺憾的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.66,0:04:05.97,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,櫻庭學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.66,0:04:13.18,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,是啊 我是正義的魔法少女彩虹由莉佳
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.15,0:04:15.72,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,來吧 天使
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.24,0:04:19.12,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,這正是Cosplay之神創造的奇跡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.61,0:04:30.45,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,原來是這樣 你和朋友吵架了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.69,0:04:34.35,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,是 那傢伙生氣出門之後就再也沒回來
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.79,0:04:36.28,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,你大概知道是什麼原因嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.33,0:04:39.36,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,要是說有的話 還是有的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.66,0:04:40.49,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.57,0:04:42.44,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,的確 我們是敵人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.06,0:04:45.08,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,我只是說出了事實
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.55,0:04:47.84,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,不過看來似乎傷到她了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.84,0:04:49.76,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,事實…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.78,0:04:54.16,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,可是在這之前我們也一直為同樣的事爭吵的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.77,0:04:56.94,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,所以說她到底為什麼那麼生氣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.16,0:04:59.32,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,我實在是搞不懂她的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.03,0:05:04.51,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,我應該能理解那位的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.27,0:05:12.42,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,快打開 放我出去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.14,0:05:14.59,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,快放我出去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.96,0:05:17.79,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,我絕不會讓你們賣掉的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.59,0:05:22.56,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,你也差不多放棄了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.79,0:05:23.61,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,你…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.75,0:05:25.89,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,好啦好啦 別一副那樣的表情
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.16,0:05:30.16,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,說不定你被賣去的還會是個舒心的地方呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.64,0:05:32.11,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,那怎麼可能會是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.29,0:05:35.80,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,那你有可歸之處嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.30,0:05:37.05,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.05,0:05:41.25,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,我可是有可樂娜莊106號室這個家的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.97,0:05:46.63,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,那裡的居民想必覺得十分麻煩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.69,0:05:47.54,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,麻煩？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.83,0:05:53.25,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,哎呀 你該不會是以為自己會受歡迎吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.45,0:05:55.93,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,你想想看嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.13,0:06:02.30,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,有幽靈的房間又有誰會想住呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.52,0:06:03.30,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,那…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.51,0:06:06.62,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,那種事情…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.26,0:06:11.49,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,對於活著的人來說 我們只會是麻煩
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.89,0:06:13.16,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,麻煩…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.00,0:06:17.54,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,可是 我…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.22,0:06:21.01,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,你覺得符咒和護身符為什麼會好賣
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.65,0:06:25.59,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,是為了讓我們遠離他們的身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.14,0:06:30.37,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,也就是說 活著的人就算認可我們的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.66,0:06:32.06,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,也不會接受我們的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.80,0:06:33.62,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,絕對
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.45,0:06:42.74,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,這就是事實
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.88,0:06:45.95,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,這就是…事實…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.81,0:06:54.58,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,聽好了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.96,0:06:58.82,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,我和里見是同一個社團裡學姐和學弟吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.20,0:06:59.71,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.28,0:07:03.46,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,但是也可以這麼說
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.24,0:07:08.85,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,我和里見只是同屬於一個社團的毫無關係的人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.21,0:07:11.42,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,誒 不過這…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.67,0:07:13.07,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,但是是事實吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.32,0:07:15.12,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,雖然這麼說
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.55,0:07:18.10,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,不過如果現在里見這樣對我說的話
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.31,0:07:19.44,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,我會傷心的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.99,0:07:22.41,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,里見你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.28,0:07:24.89,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,我也不喜歡
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.17,0:07:28.72,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,但是里見卻對那位做了同樣的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.39,0:07:31.87,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,即使那是事實
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.34,0:07:34.85,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,隨著彼此之間的時間不斷累積
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.93,0:07:36.58,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,看法也會有所不同
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.49,0:07:41.11,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,正如我希望里見把我當成朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.35,0:07:42.37,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,那位也一樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.19,0:07:45.08,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,那傢伙對我…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.84,0:07:46.72,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,我說錯了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.92,0:07:48.26,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,不 可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.63,0:07:51.73,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,那麼里見是因為擔心毫無關係的陌生人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.16,0:07:53.84,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,一直找到這裡來的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.42,0:08:06.34,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,謝謝你 櫻庭學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.70,0:08:19.26,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,早苗 喂 你在哪
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.37,0:08:26.82,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,哎呀 里見同學 又見面了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.42,0:08:31.62,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,那個 這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.09,0:08:33.67,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,正巧碰見了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.82,0:08:34.63,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,我說過的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.70,0:08:37.17,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,要把由莉佳同學牢牢抓住
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.32,0:08:38.51,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,牢牢抓住啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.30,0:08:42.64,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 由莉佳？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.28,0:08:45.99,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,那個
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.34,0:08:49.36,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,能讓我和由莉佳單獨說會話嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.62,0:08:51.70,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,是可以啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.58,0:08:54.54,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,幽靈獵人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.94,0:08:56.04,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.32,0:08:58.40,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,今天一大堆像妖怪的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.49,0:09:01.03,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,一下就把早苗給抓走了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.16,0:09:01.02,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}妖怪…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.11,0:09:03.09,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,好的 我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.39,0:09:04.32,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,多謝你的情報
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.38,0:09:06.93,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,里見同學 我呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.58,0:09:10.73,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,也救救我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.79,0:09:11.50,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,什麼!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.36,0:09:14.27,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,早苗被昨天的那兩個變態…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.57,0:09:17.14,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 昨天襲擊你們也是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.38,0:09:19.18,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,目標其實是早苗吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.37,0:09:20.07,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,居然是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.47,0:09:25.22,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,而且因為有一堆幽靈手下 早苗她沒能逃走
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.68,0:09:29.58,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,原來如此 敵人是幽靈嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.00,0:09:33.41,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,但首先要找到早苗大人的行蹤才行
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.73,0:09:35.74,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,那樣的話正好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.98,0:09:40.24,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,是幽靈探測機哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.45,0:09:43.45,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,有了這個就能找到早苗在哪里了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.77,0:09:44.78,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,幹得好 靜香
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.44,0:09:46.45,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,一起加油吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.80,0:09:52.42,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,好 拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.05,0:10:09.20,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,為什麼會爆炸
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.54,0:10:12.35,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,靈子力振子運轉不良呵
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.64,0:10:16.35,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,振子結構沒能承受住經年的劣化呵
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.70,0:10:18.00,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,請說日語 謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.13,0:10:19.58,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.83,0:10:21.89,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,不 這不是靜香的錯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.29,0:10:24.50,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,比起這個應該想善後之策才是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.14,0:10:27.73,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,但是憑我們的技術
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.89,0:10:29.48,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,那麼這裡就交給我們吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.81,0:10:30.85,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,卡拉瑪 可拉瑪
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.15,0:10:32.34,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,好的呵
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.77,0:10:33.92,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,超光線
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.40,0:10:43.01,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.52,0:10:48.41,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,別擔心 只是想賣你個人情罷了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.32,0:10:52.40,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,見義而不勇為 會讓我瑪斯蒂爾家族的蒙羞
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.53,0:10:56.74,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,我只是無法原諒對女性出手的惡劣行徑罷了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.94,0:10:58.29,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,交給我們吧 里見同學
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.80,0:11:02.48,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,這種專門針對幽靈的變態 就由我們來解決
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.48,0:11:05.20,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,你們幾個…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.43,0:11:08.36,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,掃描完成了呵 準備好了呵
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.48,0:11:10.53,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,好 去奪回早苗吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.73,0:11:11.53,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,噢！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.32,0:11:23.37,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,真是可憐
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.01,0:11:29.65,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,沒用的 再怎麼等 你等的人也不會來的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.99,0:11:32.23,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,我才沒有在等誰
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.32,0:11:34.74,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,說謊 看你的臉就明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.43,0:11:37.12,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,你還在期待著
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.36,0:11:41.86,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,多半是被別人說能信任的只有你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.01,0:11:43.38,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,就這樣被人家騙了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.56,0:11:46.18,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼可能 孝太郎他…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.21,0:11:47.93,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,想說他不會背叛你?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.21,0:11:54.17,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,你的心情我懂
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.01,0:11:56.98,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,我曾經也經歷過
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.73,0:12:02.38,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,就是這嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.73,0:12:07.26,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,我以前也這樣等過我重要的人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.60,0:12:09.78,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,但是被背叛了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.45,0:12:11.97,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,還覺得我消失了才好 就這麼被拋棄了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.74,0:12:14.24,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,所以千萬別有所期待
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.12,0:12:17.75,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,連能回的家等待的人都沒有的可悲的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.08,0:12:19.89,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,這就是我們幽靈
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.01,0:12:23.38,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,能回的家 等待的人也……
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.80,0:12:27.12,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,活著的人和幽靈終究是敵人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.60,0:12:30.07,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,思念是無法傳達也不會有結果的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.99,0:12:33.17,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,大哥 不好了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.30,0:12:35.11,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,上面設的陷阱都…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.20,0:12:35.96,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,你說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.10,0:12:41.41,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,哼 不足為道
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.35,0:12:44.24,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,是不是有點過火了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.44,0:12:45.22,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,確實…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.41,0:12:46.53,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,卡拉瑪 可拉瑪
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.88,0:12:49.02,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,呵 地下還有空間呵
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.02,0:12:50.85,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,前面有樓梯呵
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.03,0:12:51.41,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.28,0:13:07.29,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.82,0:13:10.51,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,我 不會認輸的 櫻庭學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.31,0:13:13.02,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,加油 由莉佳
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.23,0:13:14.80,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,加～油～
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.40,0:13:18.53,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,他們要來了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.73,0:13:21.60,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,切 果然還是要用那群亡魂嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.45,0:13:23.85,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,難道是孝太郎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.43,0:13:28.45,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,但是我們是敵人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.92,0:13:30.51,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,就算關係變再好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.98,0:13:33.22,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,最後也還是會被認為是麻煩被討厭
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.66,0:13:37.55,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,我不要那樣 更加不要
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.12,0:13:44.57,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,早苗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.60,0:13:46.87,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,孝太郎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.52,0:13:48.77,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,沒事嗎 早苗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.01,0:13:49.60,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.56,0:13:51.75,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,為什麼要來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.02,0:13:53.99,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,我可沒說過來救我什麼的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.75,0:13:58.07,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,反正你也覺得我是個麻煩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.20,0:14:00.88,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,笨蛋 怎麼可能會…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.88,0:14:04.10,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉打擾你們感動的再會
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.15,0:14:06.13,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,但是這個幽靈是我們的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.56,0:14:08.85,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,趁還沒受傷前小朋友們趕緊回家吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.03,0:14:09.92,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,正是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.25,0:14:13.24,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,別開玩笑了 你們兩個變態
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.46,0:14:15.36,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,這就把你們捉起來送警
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.82,0:14:17.76,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,真敢說呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.10,0:14:20.05,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,我們到底觸犯了什麼法律
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.16,0:14:22.74,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,都綁架早苗你還在說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.85,0:14:27.81,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,呵呵 這世界哪有不能綁架幽靈的法律
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.60,0:14:33.38,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,那麼你們問題就只是跟我們作對而已了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.71,0:14:34.50,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.75,0:14:37.73,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,告訴你吧 我們可是侵略者
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.79,0:14:39.22,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,法律與我們無關
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.60,0:14:41.25,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 差點忘了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.65,0:14:43.37,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,這個星球的規矩什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.61,0:14:45.37,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,根本和我們沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.89,0:14:47.09,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,是吧 露絲
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.69,0:14:50.82,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,房東和住客就跟家人一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.29,0:14:53.27,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,就算是幽靈也是一樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.87,0:14:55.94,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,所以把早苗還給我們
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.13,0:14:57.07,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,你們兩個惡黨
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.48,0:14:59.69,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,上 小的們
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.87,0:15:01.57,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,打倒他們的有獎金
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.10,0:15:03.69,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,獎金
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.07,0:15:06.77,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,要保護小早呵
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.96,0:15:08.89,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,不會讓你們碰到一根毫毛呵
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.03,0:15:10.29,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,陶俑光線
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.46,0:15:15.29,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,雖然是雜魚 但數量真多啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.83,0:15:22.25,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,挺不錯的消遣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.61,0:15:24.07,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,盡情大鬧一場吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.18,0:15:25.83,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,獎金
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.09,0:15:31.76,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,我拿下了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.47,0:15:35.18,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,切勿疏忽啊 里見同學
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.65,0:15:37.12,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.30,0:15:39.31,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,這裡就交給我 你快去救早苗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.38,0:15:40.68,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,好的 多謝
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.10,0:15:42.23,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,獎金
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.05,0:15:45.56,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,獎金
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.98,0:15:49.30,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,等我 早苗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.40,0:15:51.12,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,大家
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.60,0:15:52.98,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,不能相信他們哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.81,0:15:55.36,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,他們終究是敵人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.86,0:15:57.24,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,就算今天把你救出去了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.43,0:15:59.03,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,到了明天又會怎麼樣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.24,0:16:01.41,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,一定會被拋棄的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.84,0:16:04.36,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,虛偽的善意是沒有價值的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.33,0:16:05.92,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.66,0:16:11.91,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,就算是這樣 我也
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.13,0:16:14.96,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,我也
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.16,0:16:20.54,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,想要相信大家
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.14,0:16:25.17,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,是嗎 你也要背叛我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.63,0:16:28.97,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,虧我待你這麼親切
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.07,0:16:32.54,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,不可饒恕 不可饒恕
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.86,0:16:35.54,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,不可饒恕
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.11,0:16:39.65,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,聚過來吧 跟我成為一體的話
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.93,0:16:43.09,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,你們也能品嘗那個小丫頭的靈力
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.82,0:16:48.22,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,想吃 想吃 想吃
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.04,0:16:51.61,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,你們想幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.69,0:16:52.56,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.01,0:16:56.99,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.80,0:17:22.88,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,早苗!!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.23,0:17:32.74,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,這 這個
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.93,0:17:42.57,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,要是櫻庭前輩的話 一定…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.22,0:17:53.62,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,振作點 愚民
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.22,0:17:53.62,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,沒事吧 里間大人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.70,0:18:01.06,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.91,0:18:03.96,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,住手 住手
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.47,0:18:06.26,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,孝太郎 孝太郎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.77,0:18:10.21,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,救我 孝太…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.00,0:18:12.63,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,早苗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.94,0:18:20.50,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,小丫頭的靈力都湧出來了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.08,0:18:24.23,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,你這傢伙 竟敢把早苗給
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.55,0:18:27.20,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,她是我的了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.20,0:18:28.03,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,休想得逞
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.69,0:18:33.36,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,一定還有什麼辦法的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.61,0:18:41.64,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,拜託了 奶奶
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.36,0:18:50.17,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,惡靈退散
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.77,0:18:52.97,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,上了 天使光圈
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.49,0:19:01.44,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,Bind undead•Modifier•Huge area effect•and•Casting time four times!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.98,0:19:08.65,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,奏效了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.01,0:19:21.76,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,真的好嗎 要是用這個的話
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.11,0:19:24.29,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,這小丫頭也會被消滅的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.80,0:19:28.74,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,真是不湊巧 我家的早苗才不是那麼弱小的幽靈
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.12,0:19:35.29,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,我知道的 這個是絕對不會傷害到早苗的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.84,0:19:40.68,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,所以說 早苗我就拿回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.73,0:19:54.26,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,早苗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.74,0:20:00.00,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,咦 我這是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.38,0:20:14.08,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,欸 沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.90,0:20:32.96,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,是啊 是這樣的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.48,0:20:36.63,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,我們是敵人 但不僅僅是敵人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.58,0:20:45.01,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,這是我的 是我們的護身符
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.05,0:20:48.87,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,喂 你怎麼哭啦 哪里痛嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.05,0:20:51.25,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,愚民 你怎麼又弄哭她了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.02,0:20:55.81,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,該不會是你又對早苗說了什麼過分的話了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.15,0:20:57.28,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,不不 我沒有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.33,0:20:59.06,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,太讓我失望了 里間大人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.25,0:21:04.18,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.25,0:21:04.18,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs20}所以說你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.25,0:21:04.18,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs20}里見大人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.43,0:21:10.25,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,孝太郎 大家 謝謝了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.74,0:21:15.49,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,累死了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.01,0:21:19.38,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,真是夠慘啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.74,0:21:21.47,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,真是的 他們是什麼人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.65,0:21:22.56,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,想知道麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.94,0:21:26.93,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,是用靈波光線織的網呵
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.12,0:21:28.82,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,這下你們逃不掉了呵
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.88,0:21:31.89,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,下面就是懲罰的時間了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.24,0:21:35.42,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,不要啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.88,0:21:40.87,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,是嗎 已經和好啦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.93,0:21:42.93,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,是的 多虧了前輩的福
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.09,0:21:44.26,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,十分感謝
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.01,0:21:45.93,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,真是太好了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.17,0:21:46.78,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.78,0:21:47.22,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.32,0:21:53.44,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,你來給我搗亂了麼
